Open Group Policy Management (Server Manager > Tools)
Expand Forest ad.lab > Domains > ad.lab > DemoCorp_Root

GPO #1: An Acceptable User Policy Banner (Applies to everyone)
  - Standard corporate policy that shows an acceptable use policy warning before anyone logs in

1. Right click DemoCorp_Root and select Create a GPO in this domain, and Link it here...
2. Name it: All_Company_AUP
3. Right click the new policy and select Edit
4. Navigate to: Computer Configuration > Policies > Winodws Settings > Security Settings > Local Policies > Security Options
5. Edit these two settings:
    - Interactive logon: Message title for users attempting to log on. Set this to: 'Security Warning'
    - Interactive logon: Message text for users attempting to log on. Set this to: 'This system if for authorized use only.  Users much obey the Accecptable Use Policty'
6. Click OK and close the editor


